data.description: MAJOR PRICE REDUCTION!!! Charming and updated Single Story in one of the Conejo Valley's most wonderful neighborhoods!  This open floorplan has 4 good size bedroom and two full baths. This is the property you have been waiting for!  The remodeled kitchen opens to the family room and has beautiful newer cabinets and granite countertops with breakfast bar, next to the kitchen is the laundry room with a large walk in pantry.  The bathrooms have pretty cabinets, granite countertops and recessed lighting. Newer dual pane windows, attractive flooring and 4 sliding doors add to the ambiance of bringing the outside light into the home.  There is a large peaceful private backyard with very large covered patio.  Many different mature fruit trees from pomegranate, avocado, and citrus to name a few.  The property has deep side yards for added privacy. $60,000 Solar Panel System is Included! The property is close to everything including the Oak's Mall, many restaurants, hiking, biking, Los Robles Golf Course, Lynn Oaks park and top-rated schools. Come and see this for yourself!  Don't miss the wonderful PARK at the top of the street!!!
